Package org.sd.text

Interface Summary
PatternFinder Interface for finding patterns in text.
SplitterFactory Factory interface for creating WordGramSplitter instances.
TextSegmenter Interface for segmenting text into phrases suitable for splitting out Word N-Grams.
TextSegmenterFactory Factory interface for creating TextSegmenter instances for text.
TextSplitter Interface for splitting text.
Trie Implementation of a trie for string matching.
WordGramSplitter Utility to split a string into N-word grams.
WordGramSplitter.WordAcceptor Interface for accepting a word.
WordGramStat.NGramAcceptor Interface used for collecting NGrams to determine which to accept.
 

Class Summary
AbstractPatternFinder Abstract implementation of a pattern finder.
AbstractWordGramSplitter Abstract implementation of the WordGramSplitter interface.
AsianWordGramSplitter WordGramSplitter for splitting asian character strings into N-words grams.
BruteForceTrie Implementation of a trie for string matching.
CapitalizedPhraseSplitter A WordGramSplitter for extracting capitalized phrases from text.
DefaultSplitterFactory Default implementation of the SplitterFactory interface to generate DefaultWordGramSplitter instances.
DefaultWordGramSplitter Utility to split a string into N-word grams.
DetailedUrl Utility wrapper around a url that gives detailed access to its pieces.
EditDistance Utility to compute the edit distance between two strings.
FreqOnomasticon An onomasticon (names database) with frequencies attached to the names.
FreqOnomasticon.FreqName Data structure to hold a name with its frequency info.
GeneralTextSegmenter A general text segmenter that uses a general SentenceIterator for locale-based sentence segmentation.
GeneralWordAcceptor A general word acceptor to be used by a word gram splitter.
IndexingNormalizer A general normalization implementation suitable for most indexing applications.
KeyGenerator
KeywordSplitter Class to split a string at keywords.
KeywordSplitter.Split Container for split text, identifying its origin.
MappedSentenceSegmenter A sentence segmenter over a mapped string.
MultiTermFinder Term finding utility for finding combinations of terms in text.
MungedWordFinder Utility to find meaningful words in strings.
MungedWordFinder.Word Container class for a word.
MungedWordFinder.WordSequence Container for a sequence of words for a string.
NGramFreq Container for an NGram and associated information.
NGramFreqSet Container for a set of NGrams sharing the same frequency.
NGramFreqSetIterator An iterator over sets of NGrams with the same frequency from most to least frequent.
NGramSet Container for a set of NGrams.
NumberFinder Utility to find a number pattern in a string.
PatternFinderFunction An XmlTextRipperFunction to apply a patternFinder.
PersistentTermFinder Wrapper around a term finder to persist and re-use a persisted version build from words in a file.
RegexXtrFunction An XmlTextRipperFunction to apply a regex.
RobinKarpStringSearch Implementation of the Robin-Karp substring search algorithm.
SentenceSegmenter A TextSegmenter that uses an nlp.SentenceSplitter.
StringAligner Utility to align two strings if possible.
StringScorer A caching wrapper around edit distance functions to give scoring information between the two strings.
TermFinder Utility to find a term from a (relatively small) set of terms in any arbitrarily-sized string.
TermFinderLogicalResult A logical result container for storing the results of a TermFinderTruthFunction.
TermFinderTruthFunction A TruthFunction (used with the logic package's LogicalExpression class) for input strings containing terms according to a term finder.
TextNumber Utility to recognize and map textual numbers.
TrieLexicon A lexicon to classify complete words in a trie.
UrlFilterer Given a files with url lines and a list of mtf filter def files, dump 2 files: a filtered version and the discarded lines.
WordGramSplitter.Word Container to bundle a token with its 'accepted' status.
WordGramStat Thread-safe container for aggretating stats for word N-grams (for one N).
WordGramStats Container for aggretating stats for word N-grams (from lowN to highN).
WordGramStatsUtil Utility methods for working with WordGramStats.
XmlWordRipper Utility to extract words from xml.
